      <title>PowerShell 7 &#43; Oh My Posh Setup Guide</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/powershell-ohmyposh-setup/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/powershell-ohmyposh-setup/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;prerequisites&#34;&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Run PowerShell as Administrator for initial setup&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;step-1-install-or-upgrade-powershell-7&#34;&gt;Step 1: Install or Upgrade PowerShell 7&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;winget install Microsoft.PowerShell&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CRITICAL:&lt;/strong&gt; Close all PowerShell windows and reopen&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;step-2-verify-powershell-version&#34;&gt;Step 2: Verify PowerShell Version&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$PSVersionTable.PSVersion&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Should show 7.5.4 or higher&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;step-3-install-scoop-package-manager&#34;&gt;Step 3: Install Scoop (Package Manager)&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Invoke-RestMethod -Uri https&lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;//get.scoop.sh | Invoke-Expression&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;step-4-install-oh-my-posh-via-scoop&#34;&gt;Step 4: Install Oh My Posh via Scoop&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;scoop install oh-my-posh&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CRITICAL:&lt;/strong&gt; Close all PowerShell windows and reopen&lt;/p&gt;</description>
